properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 6 at 9:31AM EST until January 7 at 12:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Winds gusts to 25 knots and a moderate chop expected.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to midnight EST tonight.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT EST TONIGHT
